title.narrative: Country Development Cooperation Strategy (CDCS) Impact Evaluation (IE)

description.narrative: (Malawi): USAID/Malawi's CDCS Impact Evaluation (IE) activity will determine the validity of the Mission's strategic development hypothesis. This will assist USAID/Malawi in determining if its integrated approach to development enhances results, is more sustainable and leads to achievement of the CDCS goal: Malawians' quality of life improved. .FY 2016 activities include: Perform the annual stakeholder analysis;Develop, submit and disseminate policy paper; andFinalize and disseminate mid-term evaluation survey.The activity will eventually help determine whether or not an integrated strategic methodology improves development results. .
